trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects to be used with catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Består av en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objektene som skal brukes med kataloger for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescriptionCollection opprettes av de ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller i sine implementeringer av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: For hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen som ligger i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll, en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt er opprettet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Dette objektet opprettholder grunnleggende informasjon om en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, inkludert IDen tittelen, beskrivelsen og en bane til en tilknyttet ikon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: De ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller kan bruke en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektet til å vise en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollens informasjonen i katalogen, uten å opprette en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollerer seg selv.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescriptionCollection er brukt internt av webdeler kontrollen som er angitt som har en samling av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekter som brukes i en katalog.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen WebPartDescriptionCollection brukes bare når en side er i visningsmodus for katalogen.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the WebPartDescriptionCollection collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: Når en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen gjengis, den går gjennom samlingen WebPartDescriptionCollection å legge til informasjonen fra hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektet som vises katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en tom ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne overbelastning av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren kan brukes til å opprette en tom samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>kontrollen oppretter et tomt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection>objekt om innholdet i en importerte beskrivelse-fil er `null`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> objektet ved å sende i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartDescriptionCollection brukes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>metoden implementeringer i de ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller for å opprette en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects that correspond to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: En samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objekter som samsvarer med den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller i en katalog.
